query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as "count!"
                FROM users u
                LEFT JOIN user_profiles up ON u.id = up.user_id
                WHERE u.email ILIKE $1
                   OR up.first_name ILIKE $1
                   OR up.last_name ILIKE $1
                   OR up.membership_id ILIKE $1
                   OR up.phone ILIKE $1
